Title: Views: Fixed possible broken table background when using "table" layout with zoomed pages
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.4.0p8
Date: 1499170520
Class: fix

When using Firefox in the newest version (54 or newer) and zooming the Check_MK GUI pages
it could happen that the background color of the tables in some views is not displayed.
